00:40:08,173 --> 00:40:11,543
I meet a lot of wonderful people.

504
00:40:11,610 --> 00:40:24,623
♪～

505
00:40:33,131 --> 00:40:36,568
(Minseok) But still →

506
00:40:36,635 --> 00:40:41,573
When you feel lonely no matter what →

507
00:40:41,640 --> 00:40:45,577
There is no tree that will not fall after being cut 10 times.

508
00:40:45,644 --> 00:40:57,589
♪～

509
00:40:57,656 --> 00:41:02,594
(Momoko) As long as you keep going again and again and again without giving up→

510
00:41:02,661 --> 00:41:05,597
Someday the tree will fall.

511
00:41:05,664 --> 00:41:11,036
No matter how lonely or sad you feel →

512
00:41:11,102 --> 00:41:14,539
If you don't give up and try your best →

513
00:41:14,606 --> 00:41:17,609
I'm sure you'll be able to smile again.

514
00:41:19,611 --> 00:41:23,048
(Minseok) [Hey, do you know? ]

515
00:41:23,114 --> 00:41:27,052
[Character that will cheer you up]

516
00:41:27,118 --> 00:41:31,122
[There is no tree that will not fall after being cut 10 times]

517
00:41:32,624 --> 00:41:37,062
[If you keep going again and again and again without giving up→

518
00:41:37,128 --> 00:41:40,565
Someday the tree will fall

519
00:41:40,632 --> 00:41:44,069
[No matter how lonely or sad you feel→

520
00:41:44,135 --> 00:41:49,140
If you try hard and don't give up, you'll definitely be able to smile again.]

521
00:41:50,642 --> 00:41:53,078
(Momoko) A spell to cheer you up.

522
00:41:53,144 --> 00:42:16,601
♪～

523
00:42:16,668 --> 00:42:18,103
>> 亮！

524
00:42:18,169 --> 00:42:20,605
Mom!

525
00:42:20,672 --> 00:42:22,607
Bright!

526
00:42:22,674 --> 00:42:27,612
Ryo I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

527
00:42:27,679 --> 00:42:30,115
I'm sorry too.

528
00:42:30,181 --> 00:42:33,685
(Mother) I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

529
00:42:36,688 --> 00:42:38,623
(Minseok) Yes, it's finished.

530
00:42:38,690 --> 00:42:41,126
(Momoko) Sorry, I'm a doctor.

531
00:42:41,192 --> 00:42:43,128
(Minseok) No.

532
00:42:43,194 --> 00:42:48,633
(Momoko) I'm glad Minseok was here today.

533
00:42:48,700 --> 00:42:51,202
(Minseok) I don't have anything.

534
00:42:57,208 --> 00:42:59,144
(Minseok) Um...

535
00:42:59,210 --> 00:43:00,712
(Momoko) Yes.

536
00:43:02,213 --> 00:43:06,718
(Minseok) ``There is no tree that will not fall even after being cut 10 times.''

537
00:43:09,220 --> 00:43:14,592
I value those words too →

538
00:43:14,659 --> 00:43:17,596
I've lived.

539
00:43:17,662 --> 00:43:20,598
(Momoko) Is that so?

540
00:43:20,665 --> 00:43:22,167
(Minseok) Yes.

541
00:43:24,169 --> 00:43:28,673
I was a shy child.

542
00:43:30,675 --> 00:43:35,613
My father said this because he was worried about me.

543
00:43:35,680 --> 00:43:40,618
``There is no tree that will not fall even after being cut 10 times.''

544
00:43:40,685 --> 00:43:47,125
“If you keep trying and don’t give up even if you fail →

545
00:43:47,192 --> 00:43:50,195
I'm sure it will be accomplished.''

546
00:43:54,699 --> 00:43:58,636
(Minseok) Then I →

547
00:43:58,703 --> 00:44:05,210
Little by little, I was able to live positively.

548
00:44:09,714 --> 00:44:12,150
(Momoko) That's right.

549
00:44:13,651 --> 00:44:15,654
(Minseok) Momoko Sensei.

550
00:44:18,156 --> 00:44:21,092
I learned that word...

551
00:44:21,159 --> 00:44:30,602
♪～

552
00:44:30,668 --> 00:44:35,173
(Momoko) It was when my father passed away.

553
00:44:37,175 --> 00:44:42,680
That's when I learned the word.

554
00:44:45,683 --> 00:44:49,120
(Momoko's voice) I was in despair→

555
00:44:49,187 --> 00:44:52,190
He told me this to encourage me.

556
00:44:56,194 --> 00:45:00,632
(Momoko) I love those words→

557
00:45:00,698 --> 00:45:03,201
I was saved.

558
00:45:10,642 --> 00:45:12,577
(Minseok) That's...

559
00:45:12,644 --> 00:45:15,580
(Momoko) Takuto taught me this.

560
00:45:15,647 --> 00:45:32,597
♪～

561
00:45:32,664 --> 00:45:35,600
(Minseok) [I used to live around here]

562
00:45:35,667 --> 00:45:39,671
[At that time, I lost my parents in an accident.]

563
00:45:45,677 --> 00:45:50,115
(Momoko) So for Takuto→

564
00:45:50,181 --> 00:45:52,183
I'm grateful.
